! odd-syllabic
! ------------

LEXICON N_ODD !standard odd-syllable noun, eg. guohtom<->guohtom-
+N+Sg+Nom: K ;
+N: N_ODD_X ;

LEXICON N_ODD_WG !standard odd-syllable noun with CGrad, eg. vanas<->vadnas-
+N+Sg+Nom:^WG K ;
+N: N_ODD_X ;

LEXICON N_ODD_OPEN !open-syllable, eg. biena<->biednaga
+N+Sg+Nom:^WG^CDEL K ;
+N: N_ODD_X ;

LEXICON N_ODD_VH !odd-syllable with VH, eg. ålol->ullul- !!What about sarves->sarrvá-
+N+Sg+Nom:^WG K ;
+N:^V2O2U N_ODD_X ;

LEXICON N_ODD_X !N_ODD suffixes (X as in suffiX)
+Sg+Acc:a%>v K ;
+Sg+Gen:a K ;
+Sg+Ill:^VHBARi%>j K ;
+Sg+Ine:^VHBARi%>n K ;
+Sg+Ela+Err/Orth:^VHBARi%>s K ;
+Sg+Ela:^VHBARi%>st K ;
+Sg+Com:^VHBARi%>jn K ;
+Ess:^VHBARi%>n K ;
+Abe:a%>htá K ;
+Pl+Nom:a K ;
+Pl+Acc:^VHBARi%>jd K ;
+Pl+Gen:^VHBARi%>j K ;
+Pl+Ill:^VHBARi%>jda K ;
+Pl+Ine:^VHBARi%>jn K ;
+Pl+Ela+Err/Orth:^VHBARi%>js K ;
+Pl+Ela:^VHBARi%>jst K ;
+Pl+Com:^VHBARi%>j K ;





